<div class="title">Thoroughly Life Changing</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=DT&Exact=1">DT</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; DT. "Thoroughly Life Changing: An Experience with Ayahuasca (exp47451)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 28, 2006. erowid.org/exp/47451</div>

<br/>



